{"tid":1019710,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖素顏照流出　MAMAMOO Solar：我會告人","createTime":"2019-02-13T06:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T11:34:17.000Z","uid":35468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1e41d6cb491fed986b2f56d2900d7d16195c63","tid":1019710,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T06:28:24.000Z","msg":"南韓實力派女團MAMAMOO以個性灑脫、直率闖出名聲，一路走過來不免受到酸言酸語，成員們也都看在眼裡。近日，頌樂因為一張素顏照遭酸民攻擊，罕見在直播上向網友喊告，讓粉絲心疼不已。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3890/d3890899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3890%2Fd3890899.jpg&h=1dbbe315&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3890/d3890902.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3890%2Fd3890902.jpg&h=03b02226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMAMAMOO忙於各地巡演，1月底赴泰國舉辦見面會，頌樂難得露出素顏現身仁川機場，卻引來大批酸民的罵聲，她在Vlive直播裡談起此事，無奈地表示：「我看到（新聞照）留言了，大家不行那樣留言，全都是罵人的評論。」玟星回應：「那要告罵人的那些人才行。」她也接著回答：「我會告人的，我真的會控告。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3890/d3890901.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3890%2Fd3890901.jpg&h=8d3f25c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直播裡，頌樂委屈解釋：「人有化妝當然會變美，如果不化妝當然不好看，但怎麼可以那樣罵人呢。」她坦言「（因為留言）確實受到傷害」，話鋒一轉，她雙手合十透過鏡頭喊話「也拜託不要再傳那種照片了」，讓粉絲格外心疼。"},{"pid":"633878eae6801877e08d4d395c13582b9e1ff825","tid":1019710,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3890/d3890898.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3890%2Fd3890898.jpg&h=d111e38b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cfc7ad2471c50e933693b59606189754915b4f8","tid":1019710,"uid":144546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T06:32:19.000Z","msg":"剩係對眼已經咁大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3651050583c1ae8ab028914e3b996853688545ee","tid":1019710,"uid":29702,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T10:53:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75623d31cf3ebc153a6bdd376da5ee9e055dfe1b","tid":1019710,"uid":111571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:12:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb80073b4af480a9538112900e659652e84f8a43","tid":1019710,"uid":170624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"邊撚到恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲人真係鳩嗡 素顏無化妝個陣靚好正常<br />\n但素顏一啲都唔差囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韓國人啲標準係唔係高到感啊 照下鏡先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}